      "date": "2014-06-06 20:15:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b1613db2-edb6-11e3-932f-52540035b04c).  Ran 6 tests.  No failures.",
